com.intersys.globals.graphapi.globalsgraphdb
Class GlGraphNode

java.lang.Object
  com.intersys.globals.impl.NodeReferenceImpl
      com.intersys.globals.graphapi.globalsgraphdb.GlGraphNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
GraphComponent, GraphNode<com.intersys.globals.NodeReference>, com.intersys.globals.NodeReference
public class GlGraphNode
extends com.intersys.globals.impl.NodeReferenceImpl
implements GraphNode<com.intersys.globals.NodeReference>, com.intersys.globals.NodeReference

Implements a Graph node by embedding the GlobalsDB type 'NodeReferenceImpl' Note that other GraphComponent implementors extend the GlGraphComponent directly; this will not work for GlGraphNode because its GraphNode interface (Collection) conflicts with the Map interface used by GlGraphComponent.
